cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the role of implicit regularization in deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper specifically focuses on multilayer feed-forward networks, it is more likely to belong to the first two sub-categories, followed by the other three.
